query:
UPDATE pota_references SET
                    wwff_code = $2,
                    park_name = $3,
                    park_name_j = $4,
                    park_location = $5,
                    park_locid = $6,
                    park_type = $7,
                    park_inactive = $8,
                    park_area = $9,
                    longitude = $10, 
                    latitude = $11,
                    maidenhead = $12,
                    "update" = $13
                WHERE pota_code = $1
